---
title: Tex-Mex Beef Burrito Rice Bowl with Cheddar, Corn Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Dig into a bowl of Tex-Mex delights! From tender and mildly spiced beef strips to a charred corn salsa and tasty garlic rice, this
colourful meal gets a smattering of Cheddar cheese and a dollop of cooling yoghurt to bring the whole flavoursome feast together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-burrito-bowl-98f24b99.jpg
